name: 'Cure' Grime>> Glass Jar
description:
Exclusive from 'Cure' UK bring these customized glass 'stash' jars to keep your goods safe

Seal in the freshness, the flavour and of course the smell while protecting your flowers from being crushed or spilled out in a pocket or your bag.

Curing dried flowers enhances the flavour and makes for a much more enjoyable and effective end product. Say goodbye to the scruffy baggy and hello to your newest need-to-own custom 420 friendly product.

For connoisseurs or those of you who rely on herbal treatment daily, glass is the best way to look after your medicine, keeping it clean, uncontaminated and undamaged. We have chosen a silicon seal and a locking clasp in a comfy pocket size so wherever you are; looking after your herb is looking after your health!

Best of all know that every time you open this jar you helped contribute to Cannabis Cure UK bringing the truth about cannabis medicine and the stories of patients from all over the United Kingdom.

Waterproof, strong, durable and curable! 
Custom hand made jar designs and embossing 
available all with the CURE logo on the back. 
Size: 10cm x 6cm Oval shaped for great comfy pocket access

Get your Grime>> Logo or more customized Glasses

For more info email: shop@cannabiscure.co.uk
